title: Smaller download size!
body:
It has come to our attention that some of you may have been struggling to download our most recent episode owing to the file size. 

We have now changed the file to be a lot smaller (around 40mb rather than the 800mb it was before) so you should have no problems downloading it. We will make sure to continue to do this for all future episodes. 

This has been updated on SoundCloud and will be updated on iTunes via the RSS feed over the next 24 hours. 

Sorry for any inconvenience!
